description.narrative:
Award covers three outputs to support:
Reintegration of returnees;
Self-reliance of RAE;
Law on Language Use.

comment.narrative:
Department of Industry designed Annual Report of Industrial Development and contributed to drafting Tourism Development Strategy, Two-year action plan for Division of Tourism and a thorough Assessment Report for Division of Tourism; 
Tourism sector in ERS enhanced and knowledge of 139 businesses on exporting requirements and environment protection improved;
36 new jobs created (89% women).

-Ministry of Justice  effectively coordinates between national institutions in the rule of law sector.
- 25% of Kosovo judges and 30%  of Kosovo prosecutors trained on the application of human rights stands and norms (including on the application of provisions of the Law on Protection from Discrimination);
- Law on Mediation Drafted;
--Guidelines for harmonizing judicial practices (criminal and civil field) at the Basic Courts and Court of Appeal are finalized and published/ Bulletin no 2 published and distributed.
